subject: Australian Open (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: The top-ranked Rafael Nadal bullied Christophe Rochus with some powerful forehands and 10 aces Tuesday night in a 6-0, 6-2, 6-2 victory at Rod Laver Arena.
